<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of this Directive, "vehicle" means any motor vehicle intended for use on the road, with or without bodywork, having at least four wheels and a maximum design speed exceeding 25 kilometres per hour, with the exception of vehicles which run on rails, agricultural tractors and machinery and public works vehicles. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevas direktiivis t&auml;hendab "s&otilde;iduk" teedel kasutamiseks m&otilde;eldud, kerega v&otilde;i kereta, v&auml;hemalt neljarattalist mootors&otilde;idukit, mille valmistajakiirus &uuml;letab 25 km/h, v&auml;lja arvatud r&ouml;&ouml;bastel liikuvad s&otilde;idukid, p&otilde;llut&ouml;&ouml;traktorid ja -masinad ning muud t&ouml;&ouml;s&otilde;idukid. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> No Member State may refuse to grant EEC type approval or national type approval of a vehicle on grounds relating to the permissible sound level or the exhaust system if its sound level and exhaust system satisfy the requirements set out in the Annex. </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;kski liikmesriik ei tohi keelduda EM&Uuml; v&otilde;i siseriikliku t&uuml;&uuml;bikinnituse andmisest s&otilde;idukile lubatud m&uuml;rataseme v&otilde;i heitgaasis&uuml;steemiga seotud p&otilde;hjustel, kui selle m&uuml;ratase ja heitgaasis&uuml;steem t&auml;idab lisades s&auml;testatud n&otilde;udeid. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The amendments necessary for adjusting the requirements of the Annex so as to take account of technical progress, with the exception of the requirements set out under items 1.1 and 1.4.1.4, shall be adopted in accordance with the procedure laid down in Article 13 of the Council Directive on the type approval of motor vehicles and their trailers. </inglise>
<eesti> Muudatused, mis on vajalikud lisa n&otilde;uete kohandamiseks tehnika arenguga, v.a punktide 1.1 ja 1.4.1.4 alusel kehtestatud n&otilde;uded, v&otilde;etakse vastu mootors&otilde;idukite ja nende haagiste t&uuml;&uuml;bikinnitust k&auml;sitleva n&otilde;ukogu direktiivi artiklis 13 etten&auml;htud korras. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall put into force the provisions containing the requirements needed in order to comply with this Directive within eighteen months of its notification and shall forthwith inform the Commission thereof. </inglise>
