<inglise> I.4.1.4. Interpretation of results </inglise>
<eesti> I.4.1.4. Tulemuste t&otilde;lgendamine </eesti>
<inglise> I.4.1.4.1. To take account of inaccuracies in the measuring instruments, the result obtained from each measurement shall be determined by deducting 1 dB (A) from the meter reading. </inglise>
